Working with Wake County Real Estate Property Values Power BI Report, 'shell', file 10

After extracting the zip file, browse to the WakeCounty_Real_Estate_Property_Template folder and open WakeCounty_Real_Estate_Property_Template_v002.pbix  file.



The Power BI Report file is a 'shell' of the project and it will help you get started.


The 'shell' Power BI Report file, .pbix file, has the following:

  1. Overview Dashboard page - an overview picture of the project and trademark message.
  2. WakeCountyRealEstate Dashboard page - it contains an image, title and trademark message.
  3. ZipCode Dashboard page - it contains an image, title, Average House & Apartment Price Per Sq. Ft. by Zip Code images, and trademark message.
  4. Township Dashboard page - it contains an image, title and trademark message.




When finished, save project.

Click on File ->  Save and save the file to your PC / NoteBook.
